  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://v.blakesmods.com/banners/mysticalcustomization?source=modrinth\"></span></p>\n<p><a title=\"Mystical Agriculture\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/mystical-agriculture\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://blakesmods.com/img/banner/mysticalagriculture_required.png\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"display: flex;\" align=\"left\"><a style=\"margin-right: 8px;\" href=\"https://blakesmods.com/mystical-customization\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://api.blakesmods.com/v2/badges/mysticalcustomization/downloads&amp;style=for-the-badge\"> </a> <a style=\"margin-right: 8px;\" href=\"https://blakesmods.com/mystical-customization\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://api.blakesmods.com/v2/badges/mysticalcustomization/version&amp;style=for-the-badge\"> </a> <a style=\"margin-right: 8px;\" href=\"https://blakesmods.com/mystical-customization\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://api.blakesmods.com/v2/badges/mysticalcustomization/mc_version&amp;style=for-the-badge\"> </a> <a href=\"https://blakesmods.com/docs/mysticalcustomization\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=docs&amp;message=view&amp;color=brightgreen&amp;style=for-the-badge\"> </a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Mystical Customization is an addon for <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/mystical-agriculture\">Mystical Agriculture</a> that allows you to add and modify content.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Features</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Add new crops or edit pre-existing crops.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Add or edit crop tiers and crop types.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Add or edit Mob Soul Types.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">All configuration is done using JSON files. <a href=\"https://blakesmods.com/docs/mysticalcustomization\">(docs)</a></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/blakesmods\"><strong><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/fdf1b29a-987b-450e-b6d4-a16c2da8aadf.png\" width=\"1086\" height=\"170\"></strong></a></span></p>",
